Hello Naga,

Thank you for getting back to us.

Before scheduling another session, could you please let us know if you have a self signed certificate ? 

Also, have you tried to add the Certificate please navigate to the EPP UI > Appliance > Server Maintenance.
Once a .pem SSL Certificate is generated (certificate.pem and key.pem), their content can be pasted in the self signing certificate tabs and then saved.
Important, you have to include the BEGIN and END directives of the body and private key.



Looking forward for your response.

Best regards,
